  <p>
The XML Contentbase Connector (XCC) is an interface to communicate with MarkLogic Server from a Java middleware application layer.
It provides APIs for
<ul>
      <li>Evaluating stored XQuery programs</li>
      <li>Dynamic construction and evaluation of XQuery programs from Java code</li>
      <li>Type marshalling</li>
      <li>Document management and streaming inserts</li>
    </ul>
</p>
